==Introduction==
紅茶の国の駆逐艦に搭載された主砲兵装、その改良版です。<br>
可愛い駆逐艦用主砲、実戦で鍛え上げられた、優れた対潜戦闘力を誇る紅茶の国の駆逐艦達に、ASDICと共にぜひ搭載したいですね！

This is an improved model of the main armament of destroyers from the Country of Tea.<br>
It is a main gun of the darling destroyer that has been tempered in combat.<br>
The destroyers from the Country of Tea with the ASW they are proud of would like to equip it alongside ASDICs!

